{"tid":1607292,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌突然間諗到！水炮車其實有弱點！！係煙霧彈！","createTime":"2019-09-30T19:24:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T16:41:39.000Z","uid":154486,"like":190,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"d2ffa80e28220cc276ee936e3b89298a641d9d54","tid":1607292,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T19:24:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>係煙霧</strong></span><br />\n大煙就乜都睇唔到，有水都射唔到！<br />\n所以有水炮車就好少會催淚彈放題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n915有義士曾經用滅火筒救火，呢種濃度既煙已經好適合掩護<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/60TCEsYebwk?t=187\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F60TCEsYebwk%3Ft%3D187&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdbJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=8205534d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/60TCEsYebwk?t=187</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">只要係水炮車駛出黎之前所有人後退，大家再出大量兵乓波煙霧彈，水炮車就乜撚都睇唔到</span></strong><br />\n但係我地仲睇到架車既大約位置，再水火魔法侍候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n煙霧散左就再黎"},{"pid":"308c59537b7eca471342f6ec21fa3c4f0dec0729","tid":1607292,"uid":290205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T19:26:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bf88a86a88cc18bda8cb9a70d890ce356527cb9","tid":1607292,"uid":154486,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T19:27:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>兵乓波<br />\n大量</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"bc09a14e67a88b4978b47ea51ce571127ea88bf8","tid":1607292,"uid":223780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T19:28:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/